text: Manuel Rebollo García (born 2 July 1945) is a Spanish Navy admiral. He became Chief of the Naval Staff on 18 July 2008. Admiral Jaime Muñoz-Delgado replaced him on 27 July de 2012. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Chiefs of Staff of the Navy (Spain) Category:Living people Category:People from Vega Baja del Segura Category:Spanish admirals
